translate ru WhatToDoInRahayal_e6211f59:
    # "Sarah said her goodbyes to Sigmund, Sakar and Krip."
    ""

translate ru WhatToDoInRahayal_e31654d0:
    # "To her surprise, even Krip offered her a few words of good luck."
    ""

translate ru WhatToDoInRahayal_35428e18:
    # "Finally, with nothing left to be done or said, Sarah waved at the men she had come to consider friends, and walked off into the crowd."
    ""

translate ru WhatToDoInRahayal_dcfd8814:
    # "Before long, so many people flanked her from every side, she could no longer turn around and see them."
    ""

translate ru WhatToDoInRahayal_a0d97f05:
    # "She wondered if she ever would see them again."
    ""

translate ru WhatToDoInRahayal_4360bce5:
    # "For now, this is where the story ends."
    ""

